Package lt.viko.eif.m.trojanovskis.taksi.rest.taksirest.Service

Class orderService

java.lang.Object
lt.viko.eif.m.trojanovskis.taksi.rest.taksirest.Service.orderService
@Service public class orderService extends Object
Represents OrderService Object that builds Order Object and does operations with it. This class is responsible for getting, deleting, adding, updating Orders and finding Orders by different parameters. This class is using OrdersRepository, ClientRepository, DispatchRepository, DriverRepository and EntityManager to do operations with Order Objects.
